      "writtenOn": "2017-12-04T21:43:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Optional: you could get rid of “kRetry” and this loop altogether if you replaced the situations that were “return kRetry” now with recursive “return ReadNote()” calls. (They’d be eligible for the tail call optimization.)",
      "revId": "772202373065cc8d86fccb8240edc90c3a73c1d9",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
